Terre_Haute.Ohio Boulevard\u2013Deming Park Historic:
Ohio Boulevard–Deming Park Historic District is a boulevard in Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana.

Designed by architect and city planner George E. Kessler, the boulevard is 1.5 miles (2.4 km) long. At its start at the intersection with 19th Street is an entrance including a stone structure on either side of the road.
